Azure VM RightSizing — Consumption Analysis & SKU Recommendations
Description

Analyze actual Azure VM utilization across subscriptions and resource groups, then recommend the most cost-effective VM SKUs to reduce Azure spend and improve resource efficiency.

Acceptance criteria

All Azure VMs identified across subscriptions and resource groups
Utilization metrics collected (CPU, memory, disk, network) over 14–30 days via Azure Monitor / Advisor
Over-provisioned / under-utilized VMs flagged with supporting data
Best-fit VM SKU recommended per instance based on actual usage
Report includes current vs recommended SKU, estimated cost savings & risk level
Stakeholder sign-off obtained before any resizing is applied
